Name: The Meaning of Aeons
Desc: A small piece of headgear obtained once the dust settled in the Plane of Euthymia.\nOne thought may end all calamity, and there will always be thoughts that may transcend time.\nAmid all this, one wonders if Makoto's true meaning was successfully communicated or not.
